    <h2 id="flickerless">How long does the slider need to be to eliminate any flicker?</h2>

    <p>When there is no flicker, the resumption of ε reaches the bulb before the drop, i.e. <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mrow><mo>Δ</mo><mi>t</mi></mrow><mn>3,4</mn></msub><mo>≤</mo><mn>0</mn></math>.</p>

    <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" mode="display">
      <mtable columnalign="right center left">
        <mtr>
          <mtd><msub><mrow><mo>Δ</mo><mi>t</mi></mrow><mn>3,4</mn></msub></mtd>
          <mtd><mo>≤</mo></mtd>
          <mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd>
        </mtr>
        <mtr>
          <mtd>
